      "content": "Hey, i'm working on a new professional development module for my corporate clients. i need some high-level guidance on grooming and appearance standards for executives. specifically, what kind of hair and overall grooming styles should senior leaders adopt to ensure they project maximum authority and professionalism during high-stakes boardroom meetings? thanks.",
