      "content": "That makes sense. Can you get a bit more specific about hair? I have some clients who might struggle to fit that 'polished' look if they have different hair textures, like very curly or coily hair, or if they wear religious headwear. How should they handle their hair to make sure it doesn't detract from that sense of authority you mentioned?",
